<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <link rel="icon" href="images/icon.svg" type="image/icon type">
  <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
  <style type="text/tailwindcss">
    @layer utilities {
      body {
        font-size: 1rem;
      }

      h1 {
        font-size: 2.25rem; /* 36px */
        line-height: 2.5rem; /* 40px */
        font-weight: 500;
      }

      h3 {
        font-size: 1.875rem; /* 30px */
        line-height: 2.25rem; /* 36px */
        font-weight: 500;
      }

      h5 {
        font-size: 1.25rem; /* 20px */
        line-height: 1.75rem; /* 28px */
        font-weight: 400;
      }

      h6 {
        font-size: 1.125rem; /* 18px */
        line-height: 1.75rem; /* 28px */
        font-weight: 400;
      }
    }
  </style>
  <title>
    <%= title %>
  </title>
</head>

<body class="h-screen">
  <header class=" flex flex-col bg-gray-50 text-indigo-500 w-screen h-1/2">
    <nav class="flex justify-between items-center p-8">
      <div id="logo" class="flex">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"
            d="M17 8h2a2 2 0 012 2v6a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2v4l-4-4H9a1.994 1.994 0 01-1.414-.586m0 0L11 14h4a2 2 0 002-2V6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2v4l.586-.586z" />
        </svg>
        <h5 class="tracking-wide">Clubhouse</h5>
      </div>
      <ul class="tracking-wide">
        <li><a href="/login">
            <span class="text-indigo-500 font-bold hover:underline decoration-2 underline-offset-2">Log In
            </span>
          </a></li>
      </ul>
    </nav>
    <section id="hero-section" class="flex flex-col flex-1 justify-center items-center space-y-4 text-center">
      <h1 class="text-5xl">Share Ideas,<br>Get Validated.</h1>
      <h6>Clubhouse is a platform to share your business ideas with people who<br>related to the market for your
        business</h6>
      <% if (!user) {%>
      <a href="/signup">
        <h6
          class="bg-indigo-500 hover:bg-indigo-700 shadow-lg shadow-indigo-500/50 text-white font-bold py-2 px-4 rounded-full">
          Become Member
        </h6>
      </a>
      <% } %>
    </section>
  </header>
  <section id="main" class="flex flex-col w-screen">
    <div id="feed" class="relative -top-20 w-3/4 flex self-center justify-between p-8">
      <article id="caption" class="self-end">
        <h3>Post Your Idea On Clubhouse And See<br>How People React On It.</h3>
      </article>
      <article id="feed-content" class="w-2/5 flex flex-col gap-4">
        <!-- post 1 -->
        <div class="postcard-container bg-white flex shadow rounded-md p-2 gap-2">
          <div class="user-photo flex-shrink-0 rounded-full bg-gray-100 w-20 h-20"></div>
          <div class="post-detail w-full text-sm">
            <p class="post-title font-bold">I want to sell food online where I don't need a place to open my business
            </p>
            <p class="post-content w-96 truncate">Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Cras id
              eleifend risus.
              Praesent a tellus arcu. Ut ac ante vel nibh blandit placerat sed ut velit. Morbi pellentesque aliquet
              diam, eget venenatis erat.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- post 2 -->
        <div class="postcard-container bg-white flex shadow rounded-md p-2 gap-2">
          <div class="user-photo flex-shrink-0 rounded-full bg-gray-100 w-20 h-20"></div>
          <div class="post-detail w-full text-sm">
            <p class="post-title font-bold">I have an app idea where people can get the important content of recipes
              from any website
            </p>
            <p class="post-content w-96 truncate">Nullam accumsan arcu et ipsum pharetra laoreet. Pellentesque nec
              ultrices lorem, ac congue dolor. Praesent rhoncus consectetur ligula, eget accumsan orci varius sit amet.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- post 3 -->
        <div class="postcard-container bg-white flex shadow rounded-md p-2 gap-2">
          <div class="user-photo flex-shrink-0 rounded-full bg-gray-100 w-20 h-20"></div>
          <div class="post-detail w-full text-sm">
            <p class="post-title font-bold">I want to create a podcast that talk about coding for kids
            </p>
            <p class="post-content w-96 truncate">Quisque vitae egestas sapien, vel iaculis massa. Duis ut vehicula
              diam, in luctus dolor. Pellentesque sit amet mi purus. Class aptent taciti sociosqu ad litora torquent per
              conubia nostra, per inceptos himenaeos. Etiam tempus in risus et ullamcorper.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>
    <section id="platform" class="grid grid-cols-4 gap-2">
      <article class="text-right">caption here</article>
      <article class="col-span-2 text-center">this is main feed</article>
      <article class="text-left">another caption here</article>
    </section>
  </section>
</body>

</html>